{
  "id": "RAW_e543fa",
  "title": "【实践】NotebookLM 操盘手 Raiza Martin：如何做出一个不那么丑的产品",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzE5OTE3NTEyMA==&mid=2247485006&idx=1&sn=8b0f727b844253e6b00c75ada864828a",
  "date": "2025-09-06 13:01:00",
  "author": "AI炼金术",
  "siteName": "AI炼金术",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=614949be&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FBMIuxTte9jKff8l8IOicPiajsBekvYVoCKRIBY4YAa83rib7ZXTAlPVH2kOT0XjLgU8FXKdDaDqwf8Ksep2d2lgQw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"padding:0px 10px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:2px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 15px;letter-spacing: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 27px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">来源</span></strong></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Source</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 2px;border-color: rgb(242, 227, 84) rgb(242, 227, 84) rgb(242, 227, 84) rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 8px 11px 0px;margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"font-size: 12px;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">原标题：&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Everything is ugly, so go build something that isn't</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">分享者：&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Raiza Martin&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">(前 Google NotebookLM 产品负责人, 现 Huxe)</span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">链接：</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yG5d5UaGz1M&amp;pp=ygUYZXZlcnl0aGluZyBpcyB1Z2x5IHJhaXph\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yG5d5UaGz1M&amp;pp=ygUYZXZlcnl0aGluZyBpcyB1Z2x5IHJhaXph</a></span></span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">首先因为我超级喜欢 NotebookLM 啊！Raiza Martin 是 NotebookLM 的 PM，她来蛐蛐别的产品丑，还是有一定资格的。其次是因为喜欢她说的“个人清晰度”概念，最近在无数毫无关系的项目中穿梭，感觉脑子已经是一团浆糊，挣扎过程中慢慢也意识到可能只能反过来从“自己”（能力、偏好、品味、愿景……）来反推才能重新获得清晰度。最后是因为她讲的方法论和我在混沌学园讲的 AI 产品方法论（JTBD）完全一样啊，能和自己喜欢的产品经理思路一致还是很高兴的~</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;letter-spacing:2px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 27px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">要点</span></b></span><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></b><span style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Key Takeaways</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">混乱之中蕴藏着产品人颠覆式创新的机会</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">打造卓越 AI 产品的核心是“个人清晰度”</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">从用户要完成的任务出发，而非技术或界面</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">信任是 AI 产品的氧气，必须主动暴露模型的边界</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">先搞定确定性体验，再追求概率性的惊喜</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">克制是最高的审美，聚焦做好一件事</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgb(215,211,199);text-decoration-thickness: 4px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们正处在 AI 产品“笨拙的尴尬年代”</span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a05f8f2c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIY7NFO55qBuQYZhtvk5fUlNm5UhIhDJpwtOicusbGfHaF1LTvzYd2B1ZvsSbLYv25EpwQibplHMQuA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Raiza Martin: \"当前的产品，很大程度上是在前 AI 时代创造的，它们是我眼中‘最丑陋的样子’，因为它们没有充分利用 AI 可能带来的丰富交互。\"</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 10px;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Raiza 的核心论点既辛辣又精准：我们正处在一个过渡期，一个 AI 产品的“笨拙尴尬年代” (Clunky Awkward Years)。市场上的大多数应用，其底层架构和交互逻辑都诞生于 AI 浪潮之前。如今，它们只是在原有基础上，仓促地“贴”上一个 AI 功能，就像给一辆马车装上喷气引擎，显得格格不入。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">与此同时，用户的期望正在被飞速拉高。当他们在 ChatGPT 或 Midjourney 上体验到那种如丝般顺滑、心领神会的交互后，再回到那些“老旧”的工具时，一种强烈的不满和落差感油然而生。Raiza 将此称为“消费者不安”(Consumer Unrest)。</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种体验上的巨大鸿沟，正是当前产品显得“丑陋”的根本原因。它们笨拙、迟钝，无法满足用户被 AI “惯坏”了的胃口。</span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">原则一</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">万物之始，源于“个人清晰度”</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=11ca7d20&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIY7NFO55qBuQYZhtvk5fUlLicsx9Ps1PQLPiaS3d95zQzodeUgIyF23wiaJnibULutyyem0yILleLj9w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Raiza Martin: \"个人清晰度对于推动产品开发至关重要，它包含了愿景、目标和品味的清晰。这是你带给产品的最宝贵的东西。\"</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 10px;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在嘈杂的 AI 领域，如何才能不迷失方向？Raiza 给出的第一个、也是最重要的答案是：“个人清晰度” (Personal Clarity)。这并非一个空洞的概念，它包含了三个层面：</span></p>\n    <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">愿景清晰 (Clarity of Vision):</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;你到底想用 AI 创造一个什么样的世界？解决了什么根本性问题？</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">目标清晰 (Clarity of Purpose):</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;你的产品要帮助用户完成哪一件具体、重要的“工作” (Job)？</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">品味清晰 (Clarity of Taste):</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;你认为什么样的产品体验是好的、优雅的？什么是应该做的，什么是不应该做的？</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ol>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">她分享了自己打造 NotebookLM（项目早期叫 Tailwind）的亲身经历。最初，当她提出这个“以信息源为基础的个性化 AI”的想法时，团队内部充满了质疑。正是因为她内心对这个产品的愿景、目标和品味有着极为清晰和坚定的认知，她才能顶住压力，持续不断地向团队布道，最终将这个想法变成了现实。在一个充满不确定性的领域，创始人或产品负责人的个人清晰度，就是团队的灯塔和压舱石。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">原则二</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">从“任务”开始，而非“像素”</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7e08ca1a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIY7NFO55qBuQYZhtvk5fUlbR0JZkOIp4Qft3hb9ic0dVQP8zmiaoIONXNaNo2xnicR3VNvArHEElPdA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Raiza Martin: \"产品应该专注于为用户提供一个单一、完美的成果，我称之为‘目的’。\"</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">许多团队在做 AI 产品时，往往会陷入一个误区：一上来就纠结于交互界面应该是聊天框还是其他形式，按钮应该放在哪里。Raiza 尖锐地指出，这是舍本逐末。</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们应该思考的起点，是用户到底要用你的产品来完成什么“任务” (the Job)。</span></strong></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个“任务”必须是单一且明确的。用户不在乎你的界面有多酷炫，技术有多新潮，他们只关心一件事：你能否帮我完美地达成我的目的？比如，用户可能不是想要一个“能聊天的 PDF 工具”，而是想要“快速从这 200 页的财报中找到 CEO 对下季度盈利的预测”。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">聚焦于这个核心任务，并力求做到极致，这才是打造伟大产品的基石。先定义清楚那个“单一、完美的成果”，然后再反过来设计需要什么样的技术和交互界面去实现它。顺序绝不能颠倒。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">原则三</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">警惕致命的“AI 演示病”</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ff56f8f3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIY7NFO55qBuQYZhtvk5fUldsEzEmjbEbDMuqAkurWpLE0ET4nvOx4icAhm3VaUbrXjwl2DeIqIOng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Raiza Martin: \"产品不应该建立在炒作或新奇之上，而应建立在明确的目的之上。用户关心的是意图和无缝交付，而不仅仅是它是不是 AI。\"</span></span></sup><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></sub></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Raiza 创造了一个非常形象的词：“AI 演示病” (AI Demo Disease)。它的症状是，产品看起来非常惊艳，在演示视频里无所不能，但在真实使用场景中却脆弱不堪，无法稳定地解决用户问题。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种产品的通病是，它们为技术而生，而非为用户而生。团队沉迷于追逐最新的模型能力，把产品做成了一个技术“奇观”的展示柜。但用户对此毫无兴趣。用户带着一个明确的意图而来，他们想要的是一个可靠、高效、能无缝完成任务的工具。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">产品是否用了 AI，对用户来说并不重要。重要的是它能否满足我的意图。因此，</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">产品的价值主张必须清晰地建立在“我能帮你做什么”之上，而不是“我用了什么酷炫的 AI 技术”。</span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">原则四</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">信任是氧气，主动暴露模型的“边界”</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4946624e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIY7NFO55qBuQYZhtvk5fUlJBJRUxVQWtMPRs5nibhWQJeweouAdc3Mjv4lqmsKmAbfqflBj5CtI6g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Raiza Martin: \"与用户建立信任至关重要，产品应该‘暴露边缘’或模型的局限性，而不是试图隐藏它们。\"</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">对于 AI 产品，尤其是那些处理用户重要信息的工具，信任是生死线。Raiza 形象地比喻道：“信任是氧气”。一旦用户觉得你的产品不可靠、会“胡说八道”，他们就会立刻抛弃你。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">那么如何建立信任？</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个反直觉但至关重要的做法是：主动暴露模型的局限性</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。不要假装你的 AI 无所不能。当模型可能出错或信息不确定时，要用清晰的设计语言告诉用户。例如，在 NotebookLM 中，每一个 AI 生成的观点旁边，都会明确标注它的信息来源，用户可以一键溯源。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">另一个关键点是，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">先搞定确定性的事情，再追求概率性的惊喜</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。在用户点击保存按钮时，文件必须 100% 被成功保存。在这些基础、确定性的功能上，绝不能有任何差错。只有当这些基础体验坚如磐石时，用户才有可能信任并欣赏那些由 AI 带来的、概率性的、充满惊喜的“魔法时刻”。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">原则五</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在信任之上，创造“惊喜感”</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e33b1ff8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIY7NFO55qBuQYZhtvk5fUlff3icpxGgmDPcqPBJBUCw777CzajXvQzUErEtVhuZZiaRS7ibN7KvXjZA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Raiza Martin: \"一旦建立了信任，产品就可以通过意想不到的、有趣的互动来取悦用户，将他们略微推向熟悉范围之外，但又不会‘吓到’他们。\"</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">当你的产品通过可靠和透明赢得了用户的信任后，就可以开始追求更高层次的目标：创造惊喜感 (Delight)。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这里的“惊喜”并非指华而不实的功能，而是一种“恰到好处的超预期”。它应该是在用户熟悉的核心流程上，增加一点点意想不到的、但又非常贴心的“小魔法”。比如，当用户在整理笔记时，AI 突然发现了几篇看似无关但实际上观点相通的笔记，并主动提示用户。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">创造惊喜感的关键在于把握一个度：</span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">既要能将用户稍微带离他们的“舒适区”，让他们看到新的可能性，又不能太过激进，以至于让他们感到困惑或被“吓到”。这需要产品团队对用户心理有极深的洞察。</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">原则六</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">“厨房水槽”产品的陷阱</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7624aaf0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIY7NFO55qBuQYZhtvk5fUlD660CtChicLfP0kWGNmuq7k2wgM7FunMN42TOQ0c5Xurcu6aLzZdibBQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Raiza Martin: \"我反对打造‘厨房水槽式’的产品，即塞进太多模型能力。相反，产品应该展现出判断力和克制。\"</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">“厨房水槽式产品” (Kitchen Sink Product) 是指那些试图把所有可能的功能都塞进去的应用。很多 AI 团队容易犯这个错误，他们觉得模型有这么多能力，不都用上太可惜了。于是，产品变得臃肿、复杂，用户根本不知道该从何用起。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Raiza 用她现在做的产品 Huxe 举了一个反例。他们最初也想做一个包罗万象的工具，结果导致产品定位模糊，无法给用户留下深刻印象。这个教训让她更加坚信：</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">少即是多</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个优秀的产品，应该体现出设计者的“品味”和“判断力”。它会克制地只选择那些与核心任务最相关、最能创造价值的能力，并把它们打磨到极致。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">原则七</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">克制，是最高的审美</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1c8939cb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIY7NFO55qBuQYZhtvk5fUl9XvEm1FnJYxWJDroMJquRK3GmxEsE63opkJu3nPHVqRgPIzxuRSCpw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Raiza Martin: \"专注于把‘一件事情做得极其合理地好’。\"</span></span></sup><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></sub></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是 Raiza 贯穿整个分享的核心思想，也是对前几个原则的高度概括。在这个人人都能轻易调用强大模型能力的时代，技术本身不再是稀缺资源。真正的壁垒，在于你的认知、品味和专注力。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">你能否抵抗住“既要又要”的诱惑？你能否为你的产品划定一个清晰而狭窄的边界？你能否将全部资源和心力，都倾注于解决那一个核心的用户任务，并日复一日地将其打磨到无可挑剔？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这很难，因为它要求你不断地对各种可能性说“不”。但正是这种克制和专注，才能让你在当前这个“万物皆丑”的喧嚣环境中，打造出真正优雅、有用、能穿越周期的好产品。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;letter-spacing:2px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 27px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Closing Thoughts</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">没什么好总结的，这些原则都是 AI 产品经理基本功啊。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "NotebookLM 前 PM Raiza Martin 分享 AI 产品设计原则，强调聚焦用户任务、建立信任和保持克制，以应对 AI 产品‘笨拙尴尬年代’的挑战。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "NotebookLM 前 PM Raiza Martin 分享 AI 产品设计原则，强调聚焦用户任务、建立信任和保持克制，以应对 AI 产品‘笨拙尴尬年代’的挑战。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了当前 AI 产品面临的“笨拙尴尬年代”及用户期望与现有产品体验之间的巨大鸿沟。前 Google NotebookLM 产品负责人 Raiza Martin 提出了七项核心原则，旨在指导产品经理打造卓越的 AI 产品。这些原则包括强调“个人清晰度”（愿景、目标、品味）的重要性，主张从用户要完成的“任务”出发进行产品设计，警惕“AI 演示病”的危害，强调建立信任（主动暴露模型局限性、保障确定性体验），以及提倡克制与专注，将核心任务做到极致，避免功能臃肿的“厨房水槽式产品”，以实现更高的审美和长久的价值。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "“个人清晰度”是 AI 产品成功的基石，需明确愿景、目标和品味。",
      "explanation": "在充满不确定性的 AI 领域，产品负责人对产品愿景、目标和品味的坚定认知，是团队的灯塔和压舱石，能顶住压力将想法变为现实。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 产品设计应从用户要完成的“任务”出发，而非技术或界面。",
      "explanation": "聚焦于用户单一、明确的核心任务，并力求极致，是打造伟大产品的基石。先定义“目的”，再反向设计技术和交互界面。"
    },
    {
      "point": "警惕“AI 演示病”，产品价值应建立在解决用户意图而非技术奇观之上。",
      "explanation": "产品不应为技术而生，而应为用户意图服务。用户关心的是产品能否可靠、高效地完成任务，而非其是否使用了酷炫的 AI 技术。"
    },
    {
      "point": "信任是 AI 产品的生命线，必须主动暴露模型的局限性并保障确定性体验。",
      "explanation": "通过透明化模型边界、标注信息来源，并确保基础功能的确定性，才能赢得用户信任，进而在此基础上创造恰到好处的惊喜感。"
    },
    {
      "point": "克制与专注是 AI 产品设计的最高审美，避免功能臃肿。",
      "explanation": "抵抗“既要又要”的诱惑，为产品划定清晰狭窄的边界，将全部资源倾注于解决一个核心用户任务，才能打造出真正优雅、有用的产品。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "当前的产品，很大程度上是在前 AI 时代创造的，它们是我眼中'最丑陋的样子'，因为它们没有充分利用 AI 可能带来的丰富交互。",
    "个人清晰度对于推动产品开发至关重要，它包含了愿景、目标和品味的清晰。这是你带给产品的最宝贵的东西。",
    "与用户建立信任至关重要，产品应该'暴露边缘'或模型的局限性，而不是试图隐藏它们。",
    "专注于把'一件事情做得极其合理地好'。"
  ],
